title: MATES =EXTREME FUN
text: Wow !! What an amazing place to play arcade games which you need tokens to play games (more you drink the more tokens you get) but not for beer pong, and foosball table are free. The food is expensive plus paying + is the service fee. But getting a few nibbles and then sharing it among your friends then it works out well. Service is really good and helpful oh and also check out the hour drinks 2 for 1 :D.

title: Fab location and so clean and tidy
text: So close to Ala Moana centre like 5 minutes. 2 minutes away from lagoon great for paddle boarding and laying in the sand. We had 1742 and had great view with seeing the cultural performance was great cause you could see it and hear pretty well. Safe enviroment and ABC store downstairs for any last minute groceries.

title: Pineapple Express
text: Very interesting place. Make sure you watch the pineapple cutting demotration. The train is a must to do. I wanted to do the maze but they were closing :( I guess next time!

title: What an amazing experience under water !!!
text: Definitely try this activity, it is very different from other activites. The staff were very good and friendly. They only have 6 scooters ,while your waiting you get to snorkel and see turtles which was amazing :). If you have a go pro take it with you underwater so worth it. Purchase the pictures they take it comes out nicely and good memories.

title: WHAT A EXTREMELY HOT DAY !!! :O
text: This experience was different as I imagined it to be. I guess becasue when I went they had construction going on so most of my pictures had ladders and etc. I suggust to wear comfortable shoes becasue it is a bit of a climb and hot one. But apart from all of that it was amazing view from the top.

title: Amazing place! Close to a beach and shops and bar
text: Amazing place to stay, clean, close to the beach and has a pool. Great staff and speaks good English :). Relaxing place and was not a busy season but a lot of young adults. Tip: if you wanna a beach chair eat at the restaurants by the beach then its free to sit for the whole day.

title: Great atmosphere and clean, plus rooftop bar !!! :D
text: This hostel was so one of the best hostels I have been stayed in. Very close to the main square and bars and restaurants. Amazing view of the Acropolis!! The rooftop bar is good, just chill and meet other travelers. A/C was amazing nice to come back to the room where its nice and cool.

title: Good time to get some proper sleep and food !
text: We were in transit and our flight was the early morning so Emirates gave us a night to stay at this lovely hotel, it's not so far away from Dubai Airport as well. The food was amazing full buffet breakfast and comfy beds to sleep on after been on a plane for 30 hours. The staff was very friendly and helpful at late 3am, and we were a very large group of girls. Would go back and stay there!

title: THIS IS WHAT YOU CALL 5 STAR HOTEL ! :)
text: I am so happy we stayed here, the staff were amazing coming from the airport when we were tired and hungry, which they picked us from the airport. Breakfast was including for us which was amazing so much to choose from. The room service we ordered was just yummy especially coming from the airport so late at night. Right next door to the hotel is Nowzone which is a 4 level mall but it's quite expensive you would rather go to the Ben Thang Market inside and the outside one. The pool and gym is great to! :D

title: My Morocco Experience
text: I would definitely come back to stay here ! Because its in the centre of markets, food places, and very cheap to stay. I went for a school trip so we had to organise everything food , accommodation and travel also hotel staff spoke a little bit of English which helped a lot but i would advise to speak a little bit of their language.

title: Good Memories :)
text:
I don't know where to start..... It was an amazing experience going to visit the Mekong Delta, boat ride to the different Islands ( Unicorn, Coconut Island) tasting honey I got to hold a honey nest I suggest you do it if you aren't allergic they don't sting you!! coconut candy which was interesting to try it was very sweet and if you aren't to good with milk and other dairy products maybe don't try it, it might make your stomach all funny. When we were walking through the villages I must say it was very clean compared to most places I have been to. On one of the island, you get to ride a horse that was lots of fun !!
Thank you Typhoon Honey for the amazing experience and making us all laugh we will cherish all moments we had with you! :D

title: VERY SAD AND EXPERIENCE BUT INTERESTING
text: My Family and I went with a tour guide but they had to wait in the van because they aren't allowed to come. But it was an amazing place to see the about the Vietnam between American, I got emotional to see the photos of people and what they did. But it shows only one side of the war. I suggest you go if you are in Vietnam!
